The paper focuses on robotic grasping, which is a core topic in robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves fusing RGB and depth data, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of neural networks for prediction and labeling also falls under machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). Finally, the evaluation of the method on a physical robot setup suggests a focus on systems and control (cs.SY).
